<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shake-v">shake <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃeɪk/    美 /ʃeɪk/  </p>
<p>(shook, shaken)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 摇动；(使) 抖动；(使) 震动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>shake one’s head</strong>
摇头</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Shake the bottle before drinking.
喝前摇一摇瓶子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was shaking with anger.
他气得发抖。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-vt">2.★ <strong>vt 握 (手)；同...握手：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>shake hands with</strong>
与…握手</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>shake sb by the hand</strong>
同某人握手</p></div>

<h4 id="3vt">3.<strong>vt 动摇；减弱；削弱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>shake sb’s confidence</strong>
动摇某人的信心</p></div>

<h4 id="4vt">4.<strong>vt 摆脱；摒弃：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>shake a bad habit
摆脱恶习</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="shake-off">shake off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>摆脱；甩掉：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The evening walk was a time to shake off the day’s upsets.  
傍晚时分的散步是摆脱一天的心烦意乱的时候。</p><footer>2015 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can’t shake off the sun with one hand.
只手难遮天。</p></div></div>